@startuml sequence_view_history
title Sequence Diagram — View Version History

actor "User" as User
participant "VersionController" as Ctrl
participant "VersionService" as Svc
participant "VersionRepository" as Repo
database "Couchbase\n(adr_versions)" as CB

User -> Ctrl : GET /api/adrs/:adrId/versions
Ctrl -> Svc : listVersions(adrId)

Svc -> Repo : findByAdrId(adrId)
Repo -> CB : N1QL: SELECT version, authorId, createdAt\nFROM adr_versions\nWHERE type = "adr_version"\nAND adrId = $adrId\nORDER BY version DESC
CB --> Repo : version metadata rows
Repo --> Svc : VersionSummary[]

Svc -> Svc : Enrich with author display names\n(from user cache)

Svc --> Ctrl : VersionSummary[]
Ctrl --> User : 200 OK\n{ adrId, totalVersions, versions: [...] }

@enduml
